    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model provides High assurance for regulatory use. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed, and validation activities demonstrate adequate agreement with experimental hemolysis data across the primary operating conditions. The model is accepted as the basis for the hemolysis regulatory submission for the Class III VAD device.",
